query: SELECT dusun from kartu_ibu_registration where userID='user12' group by dusun

SELECT kartu_ibu_registration.dusun AS desa, COUNT( kohort_bayi_neonatal_period.komplikasi ) AS komplikasi_bulan_lalu FROM kohort_bayi_neonatal_period INNER JOIN kartu_pnc_dokumentasi_persalinan ON kartu_pnc_dokumentasi_persalinan.childId = kohort_bayi_neonatal_period.childId INNER JOIN kartu_anc_registration ON kartu_pnc_dokumentasi_persalinan.motherid = kartu_anc_registration.motherid INNER JOIN kartu_ibu_registration ON kartu_anc_registration.kiid = kartu_ibu_registration.kiid WHERE kohort_bayi_neonatal_period.komplikasi !=  '-' AND kohort_bayi_neonatal_period.submissionDate BETWEEN  '2015-01-01' AND  '2015-10-31' GROUP BY kartu_ibu_registration.dusun
